Modify material design themes and styles:
- In Android 5 Lollipop, Google introduces new designed language called Material design.
- It is introduces for both Android and Web application.

- In the AndroidManifest.xml file we can find the attribute "theme" under the "application" element.
Note: we can directly go the particular file by clicking on the "Scroll from source" icon.
- The "primary color" is used to defined the background of the action bar area.
- The "dark primary color" is used to define the background for the system bar at the very top of the screen.
--------
Go further with Material Design:
1. http://www.google.com/design/spec/style/color.html
2. www.materialpalette.com
